.\" docs/man/meow-version.1
.TH MEOW-VERSION 1 "2025-08-08" "meowg1k" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
meow-version \- show version info
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B meow version
.SH DESCRIPTION
Print the CLI version, build date, and short git commit hash.
.SH EXAMPLES
Show version:
.br
.B meow version
.SH EXIT STATUS
Returns 0 on success, non-zero on error.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR meow (1),
.BR meow-generate (1),
.BR meow-config (5),
.BR meow-security (7)
